e<ref>Past recipients of the [http://www.koreapoet.com/default/mp2/mp2_sub1.php?com_board_basic=read_form&&#x20;&#x20;com_board_idx=22&sub=01&&com_board_search_code=&com_board_search_value1=&&#x20;&#x20;com_board_search_value2=&com_board_page=2& Society of Korean Poets Prize].</ref>\n\n2003 Peasant Literature Award (for ''Jahwasangeul wihayeo'')<ref>[https://news.joins.com/article/104430 \u201cThe 10<sup>th</sup> Peasant Literature Award announced\u201d], ''JoongAng Ilbo,'' 2003.01.16.</ref>\n\n2006 Contemporary Buddhist Literature Award (for ''Maeumgyung)''<ref>Choi Jaebong, [http://www.hani.co.kr/arti/culture/book/104241.html \u201cHong Shin-seon, Jo Jung-rae, Kim Inhwan awarded the Contemporary Buddhist Literature Award\u201d], ''The Hankyoreh'', 2006.02.22.</ref>\n\n2006 Cheon Sang-byeong Poetry Prize (for \u201c''Bakwoon''\u201d and four other poems)<ref>[https://www.newswire.co.kr/newsRead.php?no=153832 \u201cThe 2006 Cheon Sang-byeong Poetry Prize awarded to winning poet Hong Shin-seon... in ceremony on June 4]\u201d, Newswire, 2006.05.23.</ref>\n\n2010 Kim Daljin Literature Prize (for ''Uyeoneul jeom jjikda'')<ref>Kim Heejin, [http://www.knnews.co.kr/news/articleView.php?idxno=903785 \u201cPoet Hong Shin-seon, Professor Hong Yonghee awarded the 21<sup>st</sup> Kim Daljin Literature Prize\u201d], ''The Gyeongnam Shinmun'', 2010.06.07.</ref>\n\n2014 Kim Satgat Literature Award (for ''Salmui ongi'')<ref>[https://www.mk.co.kr/news/culture/view/2014/10/1269681/ \u201cHong Shin-seon\u2019s ''Salmui'' ongi is recipient of the Kim Satgat Literature Award\u201d], ''Yeonhap News'', 2014.10.02.</ref>\n\n2017 Nojak Munhak Award (for \u201c''Hapdeokjang gireseo''\u201d and four other poems)<ref>Kim Gye-yeon, [https://www.yna.co.kr/view/AKR20170920039500005 \u201cThe 17<sup>th</sup> Nojak Munhak Award to poet Hong Shin-seon\u201d], ''Yeonhap News'', 2017.09.20.</ref>\n\n2018 Moon Deoksoo Literature Prize (for ''Jikbakguriui bomnorae'')<ref>Shin Hyoryung, [http://www.newsis.com/view/?id=NISX20181107_0000466680 \u201cThe Moon Deoksoo Literature Prize to Hong Shin-seon, the Poetry Prize to Cho Myung-je\u201d], ''Newsis'', 2018.11.07.</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:21st-century South Korean poets]]\n[[Category:20th-century South Korean poets]]\n[[Category:South Korean male poets]]\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Hong Shin-seon}}\n[[Category:1944 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n", "name_user": "Cyfal", "label": "safe", "comment": "spelling (Wikipedia:Typo Team)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hong_Shin-seon"}
